body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Dream Motors customer support. My name is Jonathan Ramirez. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Jonathan Ramirez, my name is Kelly Sanders.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Kelly. Could you provide me with your date of birth and phone number?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure. My date of birth is on the twenty third of March, nineteen seventy eight and my phone number is five five five eight four nine two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for the information, Kelly. Could you also provide me with your email address and home address?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course. My email address is kelly.sanders@email.com and my home address is one two three Maple Street, Oaksville.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Perfect, thank you for sharing that with me. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Kelly?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, everything is fine. I'm feeling happy with the service I've received. Thank you.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm glad to hear that, Kelly. Thank you for your time and for choosing Dream Motors. Have a wonderful day!
